description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '10 Minute Cardio Workout at Home' from the channel Jessica Valant.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: This 10 Minute Cardio Workout at Home will get your heart rate up with no equipment needed! This cardio workout is low impact with no jumping, yet will still get your heart rate up and burn calories. This is a great cardio workout for beginners and intermediate movers.
